      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# 🧱 Part A:從零寫 ReAct Loop\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🎯 我們要解的題目\n",
        "\n",
        "> 「SMT-A 產線良率掉到 98.2%,幫我找出根本原因並建議處理方式」\n",
        "\n",
        "這題需要 Agent **連續呼叫多個工具**,從多方面證據推出結論。\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🔄 ReAct 流程\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "   ┌──────────────┐\n",
        "   │   Thought    │  ← LLM 寫:「我該做什麼?」\n",
        "   └──────┬───────┘\n",
        "          ▼\n",
        "   ┌──────────────┐\n",
        "   │   Action     │  ← LLM 寫:「呼叫哪個 tool,參數什麼」\n",
        "   └──────┬───────┘\n",
        "          ▼\n",
        "   ┌──────────────┐\n",
        "   │ Observation  │  ← 我們執行 tool,把結果寫回去\n",
        "   └──────┬───────┘\n",
        "          ▼  (回到 Thought,直到 LLM 寫 Final Answer)\n",
        "```"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "5d0671fd",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5d0671fd"
      },
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### Step A1:準備 3 個 mock tool\n",
        "\n",
        "跟 Colab #2 類似,但這次我們再加一個 `search_sop` 把 RAG 也整合進來。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 3,
      "id": "6e84345c",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "6e84345c",
        "outputId": "1db73e03-9eaa-4226-98e7-0700e6765ab4"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "✅ 註冊了 3 個 tool: ['query_yield', 'query_machine_status', 'search_sop']\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import random\n",
        "\n",
        "# === Tool 1: 查良率 ===\n",
        "def query_yield(line: str, last_n_hours: int = 6) -> dict:\n",
        "    \"\"\"查產線最近 N 小時的良率記錄\"\"\"\n",
        "    records = []\n",
        "    for h in range(last_n_hours, 0, -1):\n",
        "        # 模擬最後 3 小時掉到 98.2%\n",
        "        y = round(98.2 + random.uniform(-0.3, 0.3), 2) if h <= 3 else round(99.4 + random.uniform(-0.2, 0.2), 2)\n",
        "        records.append({\"hour_ago\": h, \"yield_pct\": y})\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"line\": line,\n",
        "        \"records\": records,\n",
        "        \"avg\": round(sum(r[\"yield_pct\"] for r in records) / len(records), 2),\n",
        "        \"drop_detected\": \"良率在最近 3 小時內從約 99.4% 掉到 98.2%\",\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# === Tool 2: 查設備狀態 ===\n",
        "def query_machine_status(machine_id: str) -> dict:\n",
        "    \"\"\"查指定設備當前運行參數\"\"\"\n",
        "    db = {\n",
        "        \"PRINTER-3\": {\n",
        "            \"type\": \"印刷機\",\n",
        "            \"current\": {\"pressure_kg\": 4.8, \"speed_mm_s\": 60, \"stencil_age_h\": 120},\n",
        "            \"spec\":    {\"pressure_kg\": \"3.0~4.0\", \"speed_mm_s\": \"40~80\"},\n",
        "            \"alert\":   \"壓力 4.8 超出規格上限 4.0\",\n",
        "        },\n",
        "        \"MOUNT-1\": {\n",
        "            \"type\": \"貼裝機\",\n",
        "            \"current\": {\"nozzle_age_h\": 6, \"vacuum_kpa\": 50},\n",
        "            \"spec\":    {\"nozzle_age_h\": \"<8\", \"vacuum_kpa\": \"45~55\"},\n",
        "            \"alert\":   \"無異常\",\n",
        "        },\n",
        "        \"REFLOW-2\": {\n",
        "            \"type\": \"迴焊爐\",\n",
        "            \"current\": {\"peak_temp_c\": 245, \"belt_speed_m_min\": 1.0},\n",
        "            \"spec\":    {\"peak_temp_c\": \"240~250\", \"belt_speed_m_min\": \"0.8~1.2\"},\n",
        "            \"alert\":   \"無異常\",\n",
        "        },\n",
        "    }\n",
        "    return db.get(machine_id, {\"error\": f\"找不到 {machine_id}\"})\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# === Tool 3: 查 SOP(模擬 RAG)===\n",
        "def search_sop(query: str) -> dict:\n",
        "    \"\"\"從 SOP 文件中搜尋相關規定\"\"\"\n",
        "    sop_db = {\n",
        "        \"印刷壓力\": \"印刷站正常壓力 3.0~4.0 kg/cm²。超標的處理:1) 調回 3.5 2) 監看 30 批 SPI 3) 檢查鋼板是否需更換\",\n",
        "        \"貼裝\": \"貼裝吸嘴每 8 小時檢查。常見異常:堵塞、磨損、視覺辨識失敗\",\n",
